column3:
Pure Lab Vitamins Copper Glycinate 1mg 150 vegi caps

Helps to produce and repair connective tissue and form red blood cells.

The Canadian penny may be obsolete, but copper continues to be a very valuable mineral. In fact, it’s essential to human health. To the detriment of many individuals the importance of copper has been overlooked and overshadowed by its antagonist, zinc. When we supplement large doses of zinc (i.e. 50 mg or higher) in the interest of supporting a health condition, it competes with dietary copper for uptake into the bloodstream and can result in copper deficiency. This can affect oxygen utilization, immune function, repair and maintenance of connective tissue, and more.

Medicinal Ingredients

Copper (Copper Glycinate) 1mg

column2: SAFFRON-Safrocalm Night, 30vcap
column3:
SAFFRON-Safrocalm Night, 30vcap

ntroducing Safrocalm Night, a gentle, natural sleep aid and relaxation supplement that helps you experience a high quality sleep, with virtually no side effects. Have a great night sleep with Safrocalm Night, and start with a good morning. Safrocalm Night is formulated with a synergistic blend of traditional herbs that are proven to promote sleep, along with a combination of unique, natural ingredients with relaxing properties that you won’t find in other formulations. Dr. Mahmood Piraee, a registered pharmacist in Quebec,  formulated Safrocalm Night for his own family and friends. When he couldn’t find a completely natural, non-habit-forming sleep solution, he decided to create his own herbal blend.

Direction:
How to take Safrocalm Night: As a natural sleep aid, take Safrocalm Night before bedtime when you need it, to cope with occasional insomnia. You can also take it for restlessness or stressful situations, to help you feel calm. Safrocalm Night is non-habit forming, with virtually no side effects.  It will help you to get a restful night's sleep, so you can meet the demands of the day ahead. You can take this “easy to swallow” vegetarian capsule every day, or just when you need them most. Each bottle contains 30 Vegi capsules. Recommended dose is one capsule at bedtime, and can increase to maximum 2 capsules per night. Take it 30-60 minutes before bedtime.
